<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-1836] metadata.fetch.timeout.ms set to zero blocks forever</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-1836</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;You can easily work around this by setting the timeout value to 1ms, but 0ms should mean 0ms or at least have the behavior documented. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12764075">KAFKA-1836</key>
            <summary>metadata.fetch.timeout.ms set to zero blocks forever</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
